name: CHANGE: Customize Webpage Colors
description: Easily customize the appearance of any webpage with CHANGE, the ultimate tool for inverting colors, switching between Dark mode and Light mode, and adjusting brightness. With a single click, you can invert the colors of any webpage to suit your preferences, or switch between Dark mode and Light mode to save battery and reduce eye strain. You can also adjust the brightness of the webpage to your liking. Plus, CHANGE includes options for users with color blindness. Support the developer by donating through PayPal with a single click. CHANGE is the perfect add-on for customizing the appearance of webpages in Firefox.
